    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The select statement returns to be invalid for Oracle and Pdo_Oci. Even though we try to fix the adapter as shown in <a href="http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-1509">http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-1509</a>. The reason for that is the quoting in the select statement  comes all wrong. Also the authenticate method returns FAILURE_CREDENTIAL_INVALID because the "zend_auth_credential_match" variable has to be in uppercase to work with Oracle or Pdo_Oci.</p>

